======================================================================

                           cvt_hex2dec

             Use this function if you want to convert
               hexadecimal number to decimal number

    For example:
        Convert 0x0000000A to 0x00000010,
                0x00000F15 to 0x00003861,
                0x05F5E0FF to 0x99999999

    However, this function can only convert hexadecimal number up
    to 0x05F5E0FF. Any value more than this, the function will not
    work properly.

    See the tricks in "example/003_convertLargeValue" if you want to
    convert a hexadecimal number larger than 0x05F5E0FF, but not
    more than 0xFFFFFFFF.

----------------------------------------------------------------------

 DIRECTORY INFORMATION

     doc: Contains documentations about the function.
 example: Some basic tutorials on how to use this function.
     src: Contains source code.
    test: For testing purpose, to ensure the function has no error.

